<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5193862>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Antennocheles longisternalis sp. nov., adult female: (A) idiosoma, ventral aspect; (B) palpus, ventral view; (C) subcapitulum; (D) detail of corniculus and salivary stylus; (E) tritosternum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5193862/files/figure.png" ;
