<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5193854>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Antennocheles punctomarginalis sp. nov., adult female, legs I–IV, excepting tarsi: (A) leg I, dorsal view; (B) leg II, posterolateral view; (C) leg III, dorsal view; (D) leg IV, dorsal view; (E–H) coxae I to IV, ventral views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5193854/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5193866>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Antennocheles longisternalis sp. nov., adult female, excepting (C) and (G): (A) detail of distal region of tarsus and pretarsus II, dorsal view; (B) tarsus II, with detail of spine like dorsal setae v-1 and pretarsus, dorsal view; (C) deutonymph, detail of distal region of tarsus IV, dorsal view; (D) detail of distal region of tarsus I and pretarsus, ventral view; (E) tarsus I, dorsal view, apical sensilla not shown; (F) detail of dorsoapical setae and sensilla of tarsus I; (G) adult male, femur and genu II, anterolateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5193866/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

