<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5193852>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Antennocheles punctomarginalis sp. nov., adult male: (A) chelicera, dorsal aspect; (B) chelicera, movable digit lateroventral view; (C) chelicerae, fixed digit ventral view; (D) subcapitulum; (E) detail of spine-like setae on femur and genu of leg II, lateroventral view; (F) detail of setae v on distal region of tarsus IV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5193852/files/figure.png" ;
